  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6479506">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6479506/" class="title-link">真的是老生常谈，感觉内容太随意。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6479506"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/xpwk/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u46591140-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xpwk/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">罗成</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-12-26"
      class="main-meta">2013-12-26 18:42:24</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6479506_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  老先生一些访谈，杂文，演讲，内容很杂，有些观点重复，文化消遣阅读不错，总的来说，与老先生之前的书没有可比性。读着玩吧。感觉老先生这次两本书都不是很给力啊，期待了很久。希望退休后能好好叙著，出一部传世经典。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6479506/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
